# Google Maps API key
# Get one: https://developers.google.com/maps/gmp-get-started
# Enable these APIs in the Google Cloud Console:
#   - Maps JavaScript API (map display; also serves Geocoder + ElevationService)
#   - Geocoding API      (location search)
#   - Elevation API      (real terrain relief)
# Without a key the map shows a notice and terrain falls back to procedural.
#
# Streets & buildings overlays still use the keyless OSM Overpass API.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY
